:["post-11361","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-faith-iman","tag-companions-sahaba","tag-ease-al-yusr","tag-entertainment","tag-laughter-al-dhahak","tag-manners-adab","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-mountains","tag-parables-amthal","tag-prophetic-biography-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-smiling-al-ibtisamah","tag-strength-al-quwwah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2Xf","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":43710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":11361,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19386,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/21\/brothers-of-prophet-all-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":11361,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Companions: The Prophet is the brother of all believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI wish I could meet my brothers.\u201d The companions of the Prophet said, \u201cAre we not your brothers?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou are my companions, but my brothers are those who have faith in me\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/do-not-curse-insult-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11361,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not curse companions of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult my companions. If one of you were to spend the likes of mount Uhud in gold, it would not reach a small portion of theirs or even half of that.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3673,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19960,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/10\/27\/not-speak-badly-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11361,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not speak badly of the Prophet\u2019s companions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLeave my companions alone. By the One in whose hand is my soul, if one of you were to spend as much gold as the mountain of Uhud in charity, you would still not reach their level of good\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6217,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/11\/most-beloved-sahabah-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":11361,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Most beloved companions to the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn al-'As reported: I said, \u201cWhich person is most beloved to you?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAisha.\u201d I said, \u201cI mean among men.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHer father.\u201d I said, \u201cThen who?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cUmar ibn al-Khattab,\u201d and the Prophet mentioned other men.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-sireen-degrades-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":11361,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Sahaba: Whoever degrades Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ayyub reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI suspect that a man who denigrates Abu Bakr and Umar does not love the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3685 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633